    "Name": "Megalodon IS",
    "Details": "The IS configuration was built specifically for Spheroid and Periphery export customers, replacing all Clan pod weapons with four Inner Sphere MML 9 launchers carrying standard short range, long range and inferno munitions. The result sacrifices raw performance for accessibility and ease of resupply in Inner Sphere supply chains. CASE II protects the substantial ammunition bays. It remains the least capable Megalodon variant on paper but the most maintainable outside Clan space.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Combat Computer</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.17</color></b>",
